PN,39912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1776877554
OL,3,CTeacher had 'dark thoughts' over
OL,4,Csexually abused adopted baby, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FVarley denies all charges including
OL,8,Fmurder, assault and grievous bodily
OL,9,Fharm. McGowan-Fazakerley denies
OL,10,Fallowing the death of a child, three
OL,11,Fcounts of child cruelty and one count
OL,12,Fof the sexual assault of a child.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/12
